Package org.mvplugins.multiverse.core.config.handle

Class StringPropertyHandle

java.lang.Object
org.mvplugins.multiverse.core.config.handle.StringPropertyHandle
public class StringPropertyHandle extends Object
Used to map property string name to config node and parse string value to node's class type.
